<HEADLINE> Iran, Yugoslavia to Expand Bilateral Cooperation </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, June 12 (Xinhua) -- Iran and Yugoslavia signed an
agreement here today to expand political, economic and commercial
ties between the two countries, the private sector in particular.
</P>
<P>
