Hong Kong will continue to be a useful instrument which will
provide our country with a presence in that region of China and
will enable it to improve its ties, both with that region as well
as with the whole country," the minister said.
</P>
<P>
China will resume the exercise of sovereignty over Hong Kong on
July 1 this year.
</P>
<P>
Hong Kong was placed under British colonial rule after the
Opium War in the early 1840s. 
