KATHMANDU, June 11 (Xinhua) -- King of Nepal Birendra has
appointed Kamal Thapa as the country's new foreign minister after
accepting the resignation of Prakash Chandra Lohani, the state-run
Nepal Television announced Wednesday evening.
</P>
