<TEXT>
<P>
DHAKA, June 11 (Xinhua) -- Bangladeshi Prime Minister Sheikh
Hasina will leave here for Istanbul on June 14 to attend the first
Development Eight (D-8) Summit, according to an official
announcement here today.
</P>
